    div.logsharelogo
    div.title Logshare  
    div.subtitle Quickly share streaming log data with your colleagues
      
  div.container.gap
    h2 Installation
    
    pre > npm install -g logshare
    
    a(href="https://www.npmjs.com/package/logshare") logshare on NPM
    
    h2 Sharing
    
    pre.
      > tail -f /var/log/system.log | logshare
      Share URL: https://logshare.mybluemix.net/share/kkdgapgdx
      
    div Then share the URL for hit Ctrl-C to stop sharing.
    
